{"tid":601752,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"子瑜近照曝光瞇眼甜笑超可愛　愛上泰國西瓜汁","createTime":"2018-03-22T12:48:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T08:07:08.000Z","uid":9573,"like":10,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8dce11ce8c6a3dc881d7ea52a2557d7ab553ddf0","tid":601752,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T12:48:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imagelab.nownews.com/?w=1080&amp;q=85&amp;src=https://rssimg.nownews.com/images/5ab20a7b3a98263d614eedec_201803211532.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimagelab.nownews.com%2F%3Fw%3D1080%26q%3D85%26src%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Frssimg.nownews.com%2Fimages%2F5ab20a7b3a98263d614eedec_201803211532.jpg&h=02c4b5b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲周子瑜在IG中更新近況，PO出超萌照片。<br />\n<br />\n韓國大勢女團TWICE最近到泰國拍廣告，子瑜在IG中上傳幾張照片，她趁工作之餘順便在泰國遊玩，拍了不少照片。而從照片中發現子瑜的的妝容有些微改變，但是清新可人的模樣吸引50多萬人按讚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.nownews.com/nownews_production/images/5ab20aafa402303d5b040986_201803211533.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.nownews.com%2Fnownews_production%2Fimages%2F5ab20aafa402303d5b040986_201803211533.jpg&h=b582f36f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲TWICE日前到泰國拍廣告，趁工作之餘在當地遊玩放鬆。<br />\n<br />\nTWICE赴泰國拍攝廣告，當地天氣相當好，子瑜PO出一張坐船的照片，她身穿救身衣自拍，因為陽光有點刺眼，她把眼睛微微瞇起來，另外還跟成員Mina一起合照，兩人一起對著鏡頭嘟嘴賣萌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/204650_aba4b81679b7f58fe23b10098034cfb9.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F204650_aba4b81679b7f58fe23b10098034cfb9.PNG&h=9cfc1640&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲子瑜PO文寫下：「喜歡泰國西瓜汁」，剩下不好的西瓜建議再將它們推下海。<br />\n<br />\n子瑜寫下：「去泰國拍廣告回來了！有去搭船還有吃好吃的。我喜歡泰國西瓜果汁」看來西瓜汁收服了子瑜，工作結束後她仍念念不忘。期待日後廣告的呈現，想必屆時又會圈了不少粉絲吧。"},{"pid":"70a9ccb2c3f6f427172193fab80a1b6fba2d54dc","tid":601752,"uid":56230,"like":16,"dislike":8,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T12:56:16.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 妖怪咁樣"},{"pid":"7311fa961100d121bf9bd74990d5ba024082ae5f","tid":601752,"uid":62822,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T12:56:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e55cba44259fbd7266185800a8329a7746d77011","tid":601752,"uid":33176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T13:03:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">上陣10場比賽只入1球，山齊士轉會曼聯之後似乎仍然未找到狀態，表現開始受到外界批評。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">實用面積僅209平方呎，屬開放式戶型，成交價高見809.1萬元，實用呎價38,713元</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"453cfbbbcfb8853657d61cfa573e954081e93932","tid":601752,"uid":172915,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T13:03:05.000Z","msg":"樣衰"},{"pid":"d89c307a9b5eb47c7eab576fbc0fbfa45b8ba21b","tid":601752,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T13:03:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Dada西瓜汁"},{"pid":"925fa3e3ffcc3b8e4c99f80f635a9510753b88d7","tid":601752,"uid":72186,"like":12,"dislike":9,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T13:06:06.000Z","msg":"其實子瑜真係幾樣衰下"},{"pid":"5f9fef228ee81ebe907dfdc510ac28b2727719e0","tid":601752,"uid":3649,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T13:44:53.000Z","msg":"廿歲都未到咁快就走樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a1c5f55c5f8840a7ae5e2f5790f0894fe618f70","tid":601752,"uid":10876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T13:55:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote> 剩下不好的西瓜建議再將它們推下海。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b8de9af8e5e4de098debf531b8ff6fe4434ee01","tid":601752,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":6